# Request for Standing Offer for Snowmobiles
### Document Details
* **Document Reference Number**: WS3790185687-Doc3790495320
* **Annex Number**: 3
* **Publication Date**: December 23, 2022
* **Tender Closing Date**: January 19, 2023 at 14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: January 31, 2023
* **Expected Contract End Date**: January 30, 2024
* **Notice Status**: Expiré (Expired)
### Procurement Overview
* **Goods/Services**: Snowmobiles or Snow Scooters
* **UNSPSC Code**: 25101903
* **Description**: Snowmobiles or Snow Scooters
* **Procurement Category**: Goods and Services (GD)
* **Contracting Entity**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* **Contact Information**:
	+ First Name: Martial
	+ Last Name: Daniel
	+ Title: PSPC/SPAC
	+ Email: daniel.martial@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
### Tender Information
* **Tender Status**: Expiré (Expired)
* **Trade Agreements**: Toward this solicitation, the contracting entity seeks suppliers who are part of the Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA) and other eligible trade agreements (e.g., WTO GPA, NAFTA).
* **Procurement Method**: Competitiive - Open bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price
* **Regions of Operations**: This solicitation does not have regions listed for consideration. Suppliers must be prepared to provide services across Canada.
* **Delivery Regions**: Canada-wide
* **Attachment**: None
### Notice Details
* **Notice URL**: http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14961390?extsite=MTQ5NjEzOTBfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==
* **Additional Information**: Please access the above provided link or solicitations for further details. Only the information provided is available for inquiries. This is not a request for pre-qualifications.
Sincerely,
